## Proposal

### Please re-state the problem that we are trying to solve in this issue.

Emoji picker doesn't close on user B when user A deletes the parent message

### What is the root cause of that problem?

We are hiding the `EmojiPicker` when a message is deleted here
https://github.com/Expensify/App/blob/b30b55574bd3453c7c8d012aa39d62fe9de569f6/src/pages/home/report/ReportActionItem.js#L183-L185

But when we delete a thread parent message, the message is not unmounted because deleted parent action is a visible action. 

This is the root cause

### What changes do you think we should make in order to solve the problem?

Now we hide the `EmojiPicker` on unmount. We need to hide the `EmojiPicker` for deleted parent action as well

```
    const isDeletedParentAction = ReportActionsUtils.isDeletedParentAction(props.action);
    useEffect(() => {
        if (isDeletedParentAction && EmojiPickerAction.isActive(props.action.reportActionID)) {
            EmojiPickerAction.hideEmojiPicker(true);
        }
    }, [isDeletedParentAction, props.action.reportActionID]);
```

This works as expected

